c: 18
v: 74
t: "Tokkel ken nammay doynikik oobeeh fooreenih gexak sugen waqdi urrû luk digra awkat gareeniih kadir woo awka qideh, Nabii Muusa woh kaak assacakkuk: saytun nafsiy rooci ayyaaqe weeh umaane abe wee qiddaa?Yallal koh xiibita immay atu nummah atu kaxxa ceele waytoy umaah qaxumaane-le bahte kaak iyye"